Package: insperplot
Type: Package
Title: Insper Themed 'ggplot2' Extensions
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-02
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Vinicius", "Oike",
      email = "viniciusor@insper.edu.br",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")
    )
  )
Description: Extends 'ggplot2' with the visual identity of Insper Instituto de
    Ensino e Pesquisa, a Brazilian non-profit institution dedicated to teaching
    and research. Provides custom themes, color palettes, discrete and
    continuous scales, and high-level plotting functions for producing
    publication-ready charts with consistent institutional branding. All plot
    functions return standard 'ggplot2' objects that can be further customized
    with additional layers.
